Day	Content Focus
Mon	Deep dive: one flagship product (e.g. Gold IoT system)
Tue	Tech feature: ML placement algorithm, IoT sensors
Wed	Industry insight: schools, warehouses, compliance
Thu	Team/partner spotlight or ecosystem news
Fri	Screenshots & demos: dashboards or system prototypes
Sat	Quote or thought leadership post from founders
Sun	Vision thread: Africa's digital future

